channel.title: Cant get people to play my rsps! Help please
channel.description: Ok. I have a 317 rsps that i making. I have watch tons of videos and read tons of guides to make my rsps. Its made. But im trying to get my friend on so he can play it so i put my client folder into a rar file. Gave it to him. And whenever he tries to log on ot sayss error connecting to server. Ive set my firewall port. I have no-ip. But no matter what i try it doesnt let him get on. Can someone please tell me what i didnt or need to do.
